{"tid":1236981,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"白色恐怖。懷疑俾人錄片(求搜人)","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:48:37.000Z","uid":41257,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b885293f6921f5c062bf38e130706afecc21a865","tid":1236981,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"啱先係金鐘行完返屋企<br />\n我搭地鐵嗰陣坐關愛座靠窗<br />\n一如以往睇下連登同IG<br />\n無為以玻璃旁邊有人企得好奇怪<br />\n望一望又舉到部手機勁高<br />\n我思考左一陣然後問佢<br />\n你係咪錄緊我<br />\n佢另轉部手機俾我睇係抖音<br />\n我已經幾咁肯定佢係錄緊我<br />\n但我唔想驚動咁多人<br />\n因為報警一定係我唔着數<br />\n最後我急急腳走人 你無跟落車<br />\n求各位巴打有冇人可以搵到佢係邊個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DioB9xq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDioB9xq.png&h=92d51efc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"720087ab112d8f6e690eb5489c0e4f23f55e87de","tid":1236981,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3257f369f0244c2437754047a4022ba6154691a","tid":1236981,"uid":61398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d48e591840a80d8b7d48e0222c2f736d8bc04b58","tid":1236981,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7383a2357a47c8ce2597241034521d84c8c0da3c","tid":1236981,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e833da2ec068fb9315fa3c7d6fbd98112645b2f","tid":1236981,"uid":14189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:54:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣好撚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166a6c8d0bb5d1b8465a0d8011566ddf66062f61","tid":1236981,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"